      <h1 class="title">Privacy Policy</h1>
      <div class="field">
        <h2 class="field-title">1. Our Privacy Commitment</h2>
        <div class="field-desc">
          <p>At Kirimin, we believe privacy is a fundamental right. Our webapp is built with privacy at its core, ensuring that your messaging activity remains private and secure. We minimize data collection and provide transparent control over any data we do collect.</p>
          <p>This privacy policy explains how we handle your data when you use our service.</p>
        </div>
      </div>
      <div class="field">
        <h2 class="field-title">2. Information We Collect</h2>
        <div class="field-desc">
          <h3>2.1 Search Data</h3>
          <p>When you perform a search:</p>
          <ul>
            <li>Search queries are processed anonymously</li>
            <li>No IP addresses are stored with search queries</li>
            <li>Search history is not saved by default</li>
            <li>Temporary processing data is immediately deleted after your search</li>
          </ul>
          <h3>2.2 Account Information</h3>
          <p>If you create an account, we store:</p>
          <ul>
            <li>User ID</li>
            <li>User Provider</li>
          </ul>
          <p>Account data is retained as long as your account is active. You can delete your account at any time</p>
        </div>
      </div>
      <div class="field">
        <h2 class="field-title">3. How We Use Your Data</h2>
        <div class="field-desc">
          <p>We use collected data solely for:</p>
          <ul>
            <li>Providing search results</li>
            <li>Maintaining application functionality</li>
            <li>Fraud prevention and security</li>
          </ul>
          <p>We <b>never</b> sell your data or share it with third parties for advertising purposes.</p>
        </div>
      </div>
      <div class="field">
        <h2 class="field-title">4. Cookie Policy</h2>
        <div class="field-desc">
          <p>We use only essential cookies that are necessary for the website to function. These cookies do not track you across websites.</p>
          <p>Required cookies include:</p>
          <ul>
            <li>Session management</li>
            <li>Security tokens</li>
            <li>User preferences</li>
          </ul>
        </div>
      </div>
      <div class="field">
        <h2 class="field-title">5. Your Privacy Rights</h2>
        <div class="field-desc">
          <p>You have the right to:</p>
          <ul>
            <li>Access your personal data</li>
            <li>Erase your personal data</li>
            <li>Restrict the processing of your personal data</li>
          </ul>
        </div>
      </div>
      <div class="field">
        <h2 class="field-title">6. Data Security</h2>
        <div class="field-desc"><p>We implement appropriate technical and organizational measures to protect your personal data against unauthorized access, disclosure, alteration, or destruction. These measures include encryption, firewalls, and access controls.</p></div>
      </div>
      <div class="field">
